{"tid":118790,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"台女博士生遊日車禍死亡　遺體今日火化","createTime":"2017-02-13T09:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T04:53:14.000Z","uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"467d1b2f867975ae5571abd0079d0ae2629b8375","tid":118790,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"【不斷更新】台女博士生遊日車禍死亡　遺體今日火化<br />\n<br />\n2017/02/13 16:25&nbsp;193921<br />\n<br />\nFacebookLINEGoogle+Plurk<br />\n<br />\n日本媒體報導，前晚有台灣旅客駕駛的汽車在九州熊本縣往鹿兒島的公路上，於轉彎處撞上路旁的水泥壁，車上共有4名旅客，其中來自台北市的27歲女博士生徐子惠頭部遭到嚴重撞擊，送醫後於昨天中午宣告不治，另兩名分別為26歲跟27歲的男子，腰部跟左肩也受到輕傷。開車的楊姓駕駛則遭警方以涉嫌過失致死罪名逮捕調查。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n16:15<br />\n中央社報導，徐子惠父母已抵達日本，並於今日下午將女兒遺體火化。據悉，車禍發生當時，徐子惠昨在副駕駛座後方位子，開車的是25歲楊姓女子。車上另外兩名乘客為楊女哥哥，以及一名簡姓男子。兩名男子的腰部、左肩等受到撞傷，屬輕傷。開車的楊姓女子也受輕傷，但並無大礙，她昨晚被日本警方以涉嫌過失致死為由逮捕。車禍發生地點是緩緩向左彎的公路上，同車1名男子透露，似乎是汽車的左後方擦撞到道路左側的水泥牆。"},{"pid":"8a4d75fed0c6d31f673f544cf14354e560235bdc","tid":118790,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170213/1054900/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170213%2F1054900%2F&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEli7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c561a77c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170213/1054900/</a><br />\n點解花左小小都可以死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ec5bbfa451f2bb9c1f384a5051c32263c11a8f","tid":118790,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"因為無帶安全帶 <br />\n頭撞車頂 or 前座<br />\nHyperreflexion / hyperextension 係咁先"},{"pid":"afe35811f99f6cace4e32ee5cccebe9855a82fe3","tid":118790,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為無帶安全帶 <br />\n頭撞車頂 or 前座<br />\nHyperreflexion / hyperextension 係咁先</blockquote><br />\n如果係開左窗。頭撞泥石"},{"pid":"fad439aabf9d82af731702d0e624ac99c2fe3c9f","tid":118790,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c27bd2706b08df9e4fa786e4dd72908a6df99b","tid":118790,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91142b292d319b5ccf75c92b44e4b9eef41687d0","tid":118790,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:35:44.000Z","msg":"坐車唔好訓覺，尤其靠住車窗訓，之前香港青馬都試過有個人靠窗訓頭撞欄杆死左"},{"pid":"4b5f46a27ec6dbebfb0d53a475d8afeb84020ae6","tid":118790,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T09:37:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"220e8896b42daf9e2484c212b3b701a062822570","tid":118790,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4782faaa1d13b19dce65f88fc39815357dea0e4","tid":118790,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐車唔好訓覺，尤其靠住車窗訓，之前香港青馬都試過有個人靠窗訓頭撞欄杆死左</blockquote><br />\n5人車咁應該坐邊訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1f7a1ea38be7d77de3c6c94781814f520ce1e1","tid":118790,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會因為日本係右軚<br />\n台灣左軚, 唔習慣???"},{"pid":"7d40e5cd42faeefbef7a09342281d677291633d3","tid":118790,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會因為日本係右軚<br />\n台灣左軚, 唔習慣???</blockquote><br />\n台灣左軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"